The Finnish metal mining Outokumpu Oy close nickel refinery Harjavalta central Finland six week July August due current low price nickel market. "We consider nickel price bad moment rise slightly January" refinery sale manager Pekka Purra said. He closure mean drop production 3000 tonne 1987 year's output 17800 tonnes. The closure move cut labour cost extra staff employ holiday keep plant open. Reuter 